{"tid":1088673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比拿連：熱刺活在我們的陰影下","createTime":"2019-04-02T08:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T11:20:55.000Z","uid":173952,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a34fbbebf07d9e3db12643ac98ea87d525d064","tid":1088673,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴在本輪英超比賽中主場戰勝紐卡素，積分超過熱刺升至聯賽第三。正在養傷的兵工廠後衛比拿連（H.Bellerin）調侃同城對手，稱熱刺總是活在阿仙奴的陰影之下。<br />\n  比拿連說：「積分超過熱刺真好，他們總是活在我們的陰影之下!」<br />\n  對於自己的恢復進展，比拿連說道：「此前我和球隊一起去了杜拜，這是我下一階段康復的一部分，我每日都感覺更好，等不及要回歸球隊了。」"},{"pid":"d31ac78c188dfab462669f37e385e6b858dde7c6","tid":1088673,"uid":3194,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"人地北倫敦一哥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過係自稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有put pressure trophy櫃啲trophy塞到爆哂啦, 你地阿狗有冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3443cdc866c6cb2417e0760122b6b16d70a763","tid":1088673,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"熱狗甩轆 真係甩到on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5場和1場<br />\n本身同曼利差少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}